# ==========================================================================
#  Security .gitignore for the PUBLIC deploy artifact repo (defense in depth).
#  This repo must contain ONLY generated public web files
#  (.html .css .js .svg .png .jpg + _redirects + README). Everything below is
#  blocked so that source / personal data / secrets can never be committed even
#  if accidentally copied into _deploy.
# ==========================================================================

# OS / editor cruft
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
desktop.ini
*.swp

# Personal data / spreadsheets / exports (e.g. real Google Form responses)
*.csv
*.tsv
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.numbers

# Secrets / credentials / keys
.env
.env.*
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
*.pkcs12
id_rsa*
id_ed25519*
*.credentials
*credential*
*secret*
*token*
service-account*.json

# Internal planning / source docs that must never reach the public site
HANDOFF.md
PUBLISH_READINESS.md
DEPLOY.md
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
Agents.md
schedule.md
lp_source.md
course_overview.md
*_setup.md
*_playbook.md
*_strategy.md
*_summary.md
*_critique.md
*_proposals*.md
winbe_umegaoka_context.md
decision_*.md

# Build tooling / temp
*.ps1
_deploy/
*.tmp
_*.html